<item>
            <title>[LU-11210] Interop 2.10.4&lt;-&gt;master sanity test_160h: expected 1 GC-thread</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11210</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah &amp;lt;sarah@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/1375c17c-9064-11e8-b0aa-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/1375c17c-9064-11e8-b0aa-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_160h failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&apos;trevis-4vm4: expected 1 GC-thread&apos;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;CMD: trevis-4vm4 grep -c /mnt/lustre-mds1&apos; &apos; /proc/mounts || true
CMD: trevis-4vm4 /usr/sbin/lctl dl
Stopping /mnt/lustre-mds1 (opts:) on trevis-4vm4
CMD: trevis-4vm4 umount -d /mnt/lustre-mds1
CMD: trevis-4vm4 pgrep chlg_gc_thread
 sanity test_160h: @@@@@@ FAIL: trevis-4vm4: expected 1 GC-thread 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;





&lt;p&gt;VVVVVVV DO NOT REMOVE LINES BELOW, Added by Maloo for auto-association VVVVVVV&lt;br/&gt;
sanity test_160h - &apos;trevis-4vm4: expected 1 GC-thread&apos;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
